{"tid":1804334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"D人個口成日發出啜啜聲。","createTime":"2019-12-31T02:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:35:52.000Z","uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2f23ae6400f4ad3e30c370af627513234a83a0","tid":1804334,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"首先佢成日吹噓自己後生嚮內地受嚴格品德教育。<br />\n跟著，佢食乜都會習習聲，我有話過佢，佢話好味咪食到有聲囉，唔得呀？公司聚餐坐著佢隔離夠晒慘。<br />\n仲要佢食完嘢成粒鐘，個口仲會發出吱吱啜啜核突聲。<br />\n其實唔止佢，試過坐車後面無啦啦有啜啜聲(因為好大聲)，我以為變態鹹濕佬，原來又係D大媽，一係中抗老伯，其實佢哋個口發生咩事? 係咪病嚟架?"},{"pid":"f55b63c75599af5bf2d3657469e05334e0eab6ea","tid":1804334,"uid":59586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啜啜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828ed0eceb705af8f9753e9ae7f712991a8663e9","tid":1804334,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"摺摺聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aeed47ea1842b1b4b04182057eddd9f478600f","tid":1804334,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"嗓"},{"pid":"1116bf9e4819a4140a663170790249c2db221228","tid":1804334,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"沉日搭黨鐵<br />\n隔離個大媽一路睇殘體書<br />\n一路係度喺度「每」個嘴<br />\n嘈撚住曬 煩閪過閪"},{"pid":"39e4a22a701b177b4dc79e0e4d8819ed6f7b69ee","tid":1804334,"uid":199222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"病黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/妥瑞症\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%A6%A5%E7%91%9E%E7%97%87&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=a6ae81ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/妥瑞症</a>"},{"pid":"f24cfd7dae55bfdaccbbfa78df76fd5bc94bfa65","